  "last_post_content": "\ud83d\udd0e In-depth analysis for practitioners.\nIndustry leaders break down complex challenges.\n\n\ud83d\udccc What Are the Possibilities to Build Date Tables in Self-Service Environments?\n\nKey points:\n\u2022 For years, I created date tables with DAX code whenever I didn\u2019t have a way to create them upstream of the data flow. Now I've realised there's another way to do it.\n\u2022 practical signal for building reliable systems.\n\nWhat this means:\n\u2022 Progressive delivery beats blue-green for complex systems\n\u2022 Pipeline as code prevents configuration drift and bus factor issues\n\nHow do you handle deployment rollbacks at scale?\n\n#DataAnalyst #SQL #Redshift #Airflow #Dashboard #Tableau #SSIS\n\n\u2753 What would you add to this deep dive?\n\n#PowerBI #BusinessIntelligence #DataAnalytics #SSRS #Reporting #Looker #SSIS",
